foods.description: BUILD IT YOURSELF GINGERBREAD CAMPER KIT
foods.lowercaseDescription: build it yourself gingerbread camper kit
foods.ingredients: GINGERBREAD: ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, IRON, FUNGAL-AMYLASE, ASCORBIC ACID, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), SUGAR, VEGETABLE SHORTENING (PALM OIL, MODIFIED PALM OIL), MOLASSES, WATER, BAKING SODA, SALT, SPICES (CINNAMON, GINGER, ALLSPICE, CLOVES). READY-TO-USE WHITE ICING: SUGAR, WATER, VEGETABLE SHORTENING (PALM OIL, MODIFIED PALM OIL MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES, POLYSORBATE 60), CORN SYRUP, CORN STARCH, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, SALT, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, TITANIUM DIOXIDE (COLOR), POTASSIUM SORBATE(PRESERVATIVE), CITRIC ACID. READY-TO-USE GREEN ICING: SUGAR, WATER, VEGETABLE SHORTENING (PALM OIL, MODIFIED PALM OIL, MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES, POLYSORBATE 60), CORN SYRUP, CORN STARCH, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, SALT, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, POTASSIUM SORBATE PRESERVATIVE), FD&C YELLOW #5, FD&C BLUE #1, CITRIC ACID. BLACK ICING TUBE: SUGAR, WATER, VEGETABLE SHORTENING (PALM OIL, MODIFIED PALM OIL, MONO- AND DIGLYCERIDES, POLYSORBATE 60), CORN SYRUP, CORN STARCH, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, SALT, FD&C YELLOW #5, FD&C RED #40, FD&C BLUE #1, ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, POTASSIUM SORBATE (PRESERVATIVE), CITRIC ACID. MINI CANDIES: DEXTROSE, CORN STARCH, DEXTRIN, CARNAUBA WAX, FD&C YELLOW #5, FD&C YELLOW #6, FD&C RED #3, FD&C RED #40, FD&C BLUE #1.
